WEBVTT

00:03:27.446 --> 00:03:31.261
like the sanctity of life
or child marriage.

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:34.540
You just have no real answer
to the position,

00:03:34.564 --> 00:03:38.207
"Look, this is what I and my family
going back generations

00:03:38.231 --> 00:03:39.683
choose to believe."

00:03:40.508 --> 00:03:42.991
If Sam Harris is right, on the other hand,

00:03:43.015 --> 00:03:46.730
it becomes possible to argue
that certain cultural values

00:03:46.754 --> 00:03:49.247
are objectively wrong and must be changed,

00:03:49.271 --> 00:03:52.405
and to present real evidence
as to why that might be so.

00:03:53.421 --> 00:03:58.080
And looking forward, it impacts
how we build ethical decisions

00:03:58.104 --> 00:04:00.422
into the technologies we're creating,